<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(١٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{جَنَّتَانِ}</span> ... بُسْتَانَانِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بَلْدَةٌ طَيِّبَةٌ}</span> ... كَرِيمَةُ التُّرْبَةِ، طَيِّبَةُ الهَوَاءِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سَيْلَ الْعَرِمِ}</span> ... السَّيْلَ الجَارِفَ الشَّدِيدَ الَّذِي خَرَّبَ السَّدَّ، وَأَغْرَقَ البَسَاتِينَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(١٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ذَوَاتَى}</span> ... صَاحِبَتَيْ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(١٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أُكُلٍ خَمْطٍ}</span> ... ثَمَرٍ مُرٍّ، كَرِيهِ الطَّعْمِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(١٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَأَثْلٍ}</span> ... شَجَرٍ مَعْرُوفٍ شَبِيهٍ بِالطَّرْفَاءِ، لَا ثَمَرَ لَهُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(١٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سِدْرٍ}</span> ... شَجَرِ النَّبَقِ، كَثِيرِ الشَّوْكِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْقُرَى الَّتِي بَارَكْنَا}</span> ... قُرَى الشَّامِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{قُرًى ظَاهِرَةً}</span> ... مُدُنًا مُتَّصِلَةً يُرَى بَعْضُهَا مِنْ بَعْضٍ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَقَدَّرْنَا فِيهَا السَّيْرَ}</span> ... جَعَلْنَا السَّيْرَ بَيْنَهَا عَلَى مَرَاحِلَ مُتَقَارِبَةٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَجَعَلْنَاهُمْ أَحَادِيثَ}</span> ... جَعَلْنَاهُمْ عِبَرًا وَأَحَادِيثَ لِمَنْ يَاتِي بَعْدَهُمْ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَمَزَّقْنَاهُمْ}</span> ... فَرَّقْنَاهُمْ فيِ البِلَادِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٢٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{صَدَّقَ عَلَيْهِمْ}</span> ... حَقَّقَ عَلَيْهِمْ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(٢١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سُلْطَانٍ}</span> ... قَهْرٍ عَلَى الكُفْرِ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(٢٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مِثْقَالَ ذَرَّةٍ}</span> ... وَزْنَ نَمْلَةٍ صَغِيرَةٍ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
